{{Infobox company | name = TsKIB SOO | logo = TsKIB_SOO_logo.png | type = | industry = Defense | fate = | predecessor = <!-- or: | predecessors = --> | successor = <!-- or: | successors = --> | founded = 1946 | founder = <!-- or: | founders = --> | defunct = <!-- {{End date|YYYY|MM|DD}} --> | hq_location_city = [[Tula, Russia|Tula]] | hq_location_country = Russia | area_served = <!-- or: | areas_served = --> | key_people = | products = Firearms, Autocannons, Aircraft cannons, Grenade launchers | owner = <!-- or: | owners = --> | num_employees = | num_employees_year = <!-- Year of num_employees data (if known) --> | parent = [[KBP Instrument Design Bureau]] | website = {{URL|www.tulatskib.ru}} }} '''TsKIB SOO''' ({{lang-ru|ЦКИБ СОО}}) is a Russian small arms design bureau based in [[Tula, Russia|Tula]], Russia. It was established in 1946, and it is currently managed as a branch of the [[KBP Instrument Design Bureau]].<ref>{{cite news|title=История предприятия|url=http://www.tulatskib.ru/about/history/index.php|accessdate=15 July 2017|work=Tulatskib.ru|language=ru}}</ref> The name means Central Design and Research Bureau of Sporting and Hunting Arms.
